document_data.name: Strünge
document_data.mainbody: '''Strunge''' was the [[half-orc]] chieftain of the [[Green Moss tribe]] in [[Many-Arrows]] in [[1484 DR]].
document_data.History: Just after the start of the [[Darkening]], Strunge spoke in favor of peace with [[Luruar]] to King [[Obould XVII]].
